\c 16
\s VaIsraeri vanopiwa mana
\p
\v 1 Zvino vakabva paErimu\x + Num.. 33.10,11.\x* parwendo rwavo; neungano yose yevana vaIsraeri yakasvika parenje reSini riri pakati peErimu neSinai, nezuva regumi nemashanu remwedzi wechipiri rekubuda kwavo panyika yeEgipita.
\v 2 Zvino ungano yose yevana vaIsraeri ikagunun'unira Mozisi naAroni\x + 15.24; 17.3. 1 VaKori. 10.10.\x* murenje.
\v 3 Vana vaIsraeri ndokuti kwavari: Tingadai hedu takafa neruoko rwaJehovha munyika yeEgipita pakugara kwedu pahari yenyama, pataidya chingwa tichiguta\x + Num.. 11.4,5.\x*; nokuti matibudisira kurenje iri kuti muuraye ungano iyi yose nenzara.
\p
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Tarira, ndichakunisirai chingwa kubva kumatenga\x + Map. 78.24,25; 105.40. Joh. 6.31,32,49,58. 1 VaKori. 10.3.\x*; zvino vanhu vachabuda ndokuunganidza chinhu chezuva muzuva racho, kuti ndivaidze\x + 15.25.\x* kana vachifamba mumurairo wangu kana kwete.
\v 5 Zvino zvichava nezuva retanhatu, kuti vachagadzira izvo zvavauya nazvo; uye zvichapamhidzirwa kaviri pane zviya zvavanounganidza zuva rimwe nerimwe\x + 16.22. Rev. 25.21.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Mozisi naAroni vakati kuvana vaIsraeri vose: Madekwani\x + 16.12,13.\x* zvino muchaziva kuti Jehovha wakakubudisai panyika yeEgipita\x + 6.7. Num.. 16.28,29,30.\x*.
\v 7 Uye mangwanani muchaona kubwinya kwaJehovha\x + 16.10.\x*, nokuti wanzwa kugunun'una kwenyu muchipikisa Jehovha. Zvino isu tiri chii zvamunotigunun'unira\x + 16.8. Num.. 16.11.\x*?
\v 8 Mozisi ndokuti: Jehovha paachakupai nyama madekwani kuti mudye, nechingwa mangwanani kuti mugute, chikonzero \add chekuti\add* Jehovha wakanzwa kugunun'una kwenyu kwamakamugunun'unira nako. Zvino isu tiri chii? Kugununu'na kwenyu ngakurege kuva kwatiri, asi kuna Jehovha\x + 1 Sam. 8.7.\x*.
\v 9 Mozisi ndokuti kuna Aroni\x + 4.14-16.\x*: Iti kuungano yose yevana vaIsraeri: Swederai pamberi paJehovha\x + Num.. 16.16.\x*, nokuti wakanzwa kugunun'una kwenyu.
\v 10 Zvino zvakaitika Aroni achitaura kuungano yose yevana vaIsraeri, kuti vakatendeukira kurenje, zvino tarira, kubwinya kwaJehovha kunoonekwa mugore\x + 16.7. 13.21; 14.24. Num.. 16.19. 1 Madz. 8.10,11.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Jehovha ndokutaura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 12 Ndanzwa kugunun'una kwevana vaIsraeri\x + 16.8.\x*; taura kwavari uchiti: Madekwani muchadya nyama\x + 16.8.\x*, uye mangwanani muchaguta chingwa\x + 16.7.\x*; zvino muchaziva kuti ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu.
\v 13 Zvino zvakaitika madekwani, kuti zvihuta zvakakwira ndokufukidza musasa; zvino mangwanani paiva nerukoko rwedova rwakapoteredza musasa.
\v 14 Zvino murakatira wedova wakati wasimuka, zvino tarira, pachiso cherenje chinhu chidiki chakaurungana, chidiki sechando pasi\x + Num.. 11.9.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakati vachi\add chi\add*ona vakati umwe kune umwe: Imana? Nokuti vaiva vasingazivi kuti chii. Mozisi ndokuti kwavari: Ndicho chingwa Jehovha chaapa kwamuri kuti mudye\x + 16.4. Det. 8.3. Neh. 9.15.\x*.
\v 16 Ichi chinhu Jehovha chaakaraira: Unganidzai pachiri umwe neumwe zvichienderana nemadyiro ake\x + 16.18,21; 12.4.\x*; omeri \add imwe\add* pamusoro \add umwe\add*, \add ne\add*uwandu hwemweya yenyu; umwe neumwe atorere vari mutende rake.
\p
\v 17 Vana vaIsraeri ndokuita saizvozvo, ndokuunganidza umwe zvizhinji umwewo zvishoma.
\v 18 Zvino vakati vozviyera neomeri\x + 16.36.\x*, waiva aunganidza zvizhinji wakava asina muraudzo, newaiva aunganidza zvishoma wakava asina kushaiwa chinhu\x + 2 VaKori. 8.15.\x*; vakaunganidza, umwe neumwe zvichienderana nemadyiro ake\x + 16.16.\x*.
\v 19 Mozisi ndokuti kwavari: Kurege kuva nemunhu anosiya zvacho kusvika mangwanani.
\v 20 Asi havana kuteerera Mozisi; asi vamwe vakasiya pazviri kusvika mangwanani, zvikabuda honye, zvikanhuhwa; Mozisi ndokuvatsamwira.
\v 21 Zvino vakachiunganidza mangwanani oga-oga, umwe neumwe zvichienderana nemadyiro ake; kana zuva ropisa zvakanyunguduka.
\p
\v 22 Zvino zvakaitika pazuva retanhatu, \add kuti\add* vaiunganidza chingwa chakapetwa kaviri, omeri mbiri paumwe; zvino vakuru vose veungano vakauya ndokuudza Mozisi.
\v 23 Iye ndokuti kwavari: Ndizvo zvakataura Jehovha: Mangwana izororo, sabata dzvene kuna Jehovha\x + Gen.. 2.3. Eki. 20.8; 31.14-17; 35.2,3. Rev. 23.3. Gen.. 29.27.\x*; bhekai zvamuchabheka, bikai zvamuchabika; uye chose chinosara muchigadzike chichengetwe kusvika mangwanani.
\v 24 Zvino vakachisiya kusvika mangwanani, Mozisi sezvaaiva araira; zvino hachina kunhuhwa, nehonye haina kuva pachiri\x + 16.20.\x*.
\v 25 Mozisi ndokuti: Idyai izvozvo nhasi, nokuti nhasi isabata kuna Jehovha. Nhasi hamuzviwani kusango.
\v 26 Muchachiunganidza mazuva matanhatu; asi pazuva rechinomwe isabata; naro kuchava kusina.
\p
\v 27 Zvino zvakaitika nezuva rechinomwe \add kuti\add* \add vamwe\add* vevanhu vakabuda kunozviunganidza, asi havana kuwana.
\v 28 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Munoramba kuchengeta mirairo yangu nemitemo yangu kusvika rinhi?
\v 29 Onai, nokuti Jehovha wakakupai sabata, naizvozvo anokupai nezuva retanhatu chingwa chemazuva maviri; garai umwe neumwe panzvimbo yake; kurege kubuda munhu kubva panzvimbo yake nezuva rechinomwe\x + Josh. 5.8. Job. 40.12.\x*.
\v 30 Vanhu ndokuzorora nezuva rechinomwe.
\p
\v 31 Imba yaIsraeri ndokutumidza zita racho \add kuti\add* mana*\x + 16.15.\x*; chaiva chakaita setsanga yekorianderi*, chena; uye munakiro wacho wakafanana nechingwa chine uchi\x + Num.. 11.7,8.\x*.
\v 32 Zvino Mozisi wakati: Ndiro shoko Jehovha raakaraira: Zadzai omeri nayo ichengeterwe mazera enyu, kuti vaone chingwa chandakakudyisai murenje pakukubudisai kwangu munyika yeEgipita.
\v 33 Zvino Mozisi wakati kuna Aroni: Tora hari imwe uisemo omeri izere nemana, uiise pamberi paJehovha ichengeterwe mazera enyu\x + VaHeb. 9.4.\x*.
\v 34 Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi, saizvozvo Aroni wakaiisa pamberi pechipupuriro, kuti ichengetwe\x + 25.16,21; 26.33,34; 27.21; 30.6,26,36; Det. 10.5. 2 Madz. 11.12.\x*.
\v 35 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakadya mana makore makumi mana\x + Det. 8.2,3. Neh. 9.15,20,21.\x*, kusvika vasvika panyika yaigarwa\x + Josh. 5.12.\x*; vakadya mana kusvika vasvika pamuganhu wenyika yeKenani.
\v 36 Zvino omeri ichegumi cheefa\x + Rev. 5.11; 6.20.\x*.
